Machine learning is about extracting knowledge from data. 
It is a research field at the intersection of statistics, artificial intelligence, and computer science and is also known as predictive analytics or statistical learning.

NumPy
NumPy is one of the fundamental packages for scientific computing in Python. 
It contains functionality for multidimensional arrays, 
high-level mathematical functions such as linear algebra operations and the fourier transform, and pseudorandom number generators.
